  "summary": "Malicious code in api-changelly (npm)",
  "details": "Combosquat package mimicking the Changelly cryptocurrency exchange API. Installs a preinstall lifecycle hook that executes arbitrary JavaScript code (node index.js) on npm install, before the intended package is installed. The tarball was removed from the registry shortly after publication, consistent with a publish-and-burn pattern. No repository, description, or author is declared. The package has no legitimate functionality.",
